---
title: Availability
---
extends shared/_layout
block content
  
  // AVAILABILITY :: START
  .availability
    
    // title
    .availability__title-wrap
      .availability__title-parallax
      // (js-rellax data-rellax-speed="-2" data-rellax-percentage="0.5")
      .container
        .availability__title.t-title current <br> availability
        .availability__text.t-text-reg
          p I update my avaialbility below on a weekly basis, so you can see the next opportunity to book me in. 
    
    .container
      .avail__bottom.avail__bottom--bigger
        .avail__status
          span I currently have
          .avail__status-line.avail__status-line--limited
            span LIMITED
          span availability until Feb 2017.
        .avail__cta
          a(href="#" js-scrollTo data-target=".contact-form").link.link--yellow
            span make enquiry
      
      // schedule
      .avail__schedule
        .schedule-card.schedule-card--disabled
          .schedule-card__month Dec
          .schedule-card__fill
            //- .schedule-card__progress(width="0%")
          .schedule-card__desc unavailable
        .schedule-card.schedule-card--disabled
          .schedule-card__month Jan
          .schedule-card__fill
            //- .schedule-card__progress(width="0%")
          .schedule-card__desc unavailable
        .schedule-card
          .schedule-card__month feb
          .schedule-card__fill
            .schedule-card__progress(data-progress="80")
          .schedule-card__desc 80% avalable
        .schedule-card
          .schedule-card__month mar
          .schedule-card__fill
            .schedule-card__progress(data-progress="100")
          .schedule-card__desc 100% avalable
        .schedule-card
          .schedule-card__month apr
          .schedule-card__fill
            .schedule-card__progress(data-progress="100")
          .schedule-card__desc 100% avalable
        
    // CONTACT FORM
    .contact-enq
      .contact-enq__left
        // PAGE TITLE
        .enq-title
          .enq-title-parallax.--bg-yellow
          .container
            .enq-title__name make <br> an <br> enquiry
      .contact-enq__right.t-text-small
        p I usually undertake longer-term contracts which can mean that I'm booked-up for several weeks in advance. However, I frequently also tackle additional work in my evenings and weekends (around other commitments) so do feel free to drop me a line if you have a project you think I might be able to help you with, even if my schedule looks totally full!
        p Let me know what you need and when. I will always do what I can to fit you in.

        form.contact-form(action="#" js-contact-form)
          .ui-input-dynamic
            label full name
            input(type="text" name="name" placeholder="")
          .ui-input-dynamic
            label when do you need help?
            input(type="text" name="time" placeholder="")  
          .ui-input-dynamic
            label email address
            input(type="email" name="email" placeholder="")
          .ui-input-dynamic
            label other contact info
            input(type="text" name="contact" placeholder="")
          .ui-input-dynamic
            label Message
            textarea.autoExpand(type="text" name="message" placeholder="" rows="5")
        
          button(type="submit").link.link--yellow
            span SEND MESSAGE  
